Class ScadaFieldList

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<ScadaFieldDescriptor>, java.util.Collection<ScadaFieldDescriptor>, java.util.Deque<ScadaFieldDescriptor>, java.util.List<ScadaFieldDescriptor>, java.util.Queue<ScadaFieldDescriptor>

    public class ScadaFieldList
extends java.util.LinkedList<ScadaFieldDescriptor>
implements java.util.List<ScadaFieldDescriptor>
    This is a list of all ScadaFieldDescriptor objects parsed from a SCADA data structure. The field descriptors are sorted by the ordering encountered in the declaration of fields in the SCADA data structure.

    Ported from XAL on Jul 15, 2014.
    · Jonathan M. Freed
